  "translations": {
    "en": "The asker's right is giving according to need. The one asked: if he gives, accept with gratitude; if withholds, accept his excuse. The one through whom Allah brings joy: first praise Allah, then thank him. The one who wrongs you: pardon him. If you know pardoning harms him, defend yourself. Allah says: 'And whoever defends himself after being wronged, upon those there is no way.'",
